data.description: Spacious design, quality built home.  Main floor has original hardwood floors, spacious living room with wood burning fireplace and large formal dining room.  The kitchen, dining and living room have a very open concept feel.  Basement has a storage area, large laundry room, and a roomy workshop. Also the basement has a large family room and a large area that was originally a primary bedroom complete with 3/4 bath and closet. One wall of bedroom was removed to increase the size of the family room. The garage on southside of the house is attached and has direct entry to the kitchen.  Their is also a covered/partially enclosed carport on the other end of the house for a total of two places to park your vehicles out of the weather.
